Use the standard library
This is how to digitSum of s:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that n is s's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in s
      When x is at least 65, then:
         When x is at most 90, then:
            Remember that total is sum of total and x
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
